data.description: If privacy is what your looking for this home sitting way back off the main road is what you're looking for. Manufactured home on 4.22 acres with large storage building. 3 Bedrooms, 2 Baths with a wood burning fireplace. Home sits at the back of the property. Homeowner just installed new solar panels and permitted through the county. This should bring your energy cost down. Homeowner states Spectrum does come to the house for cable and internet needs.
